Paper: hep-th/0108088

Date: 2001-08-13

Title: A General Expression for Symmetry Factors of Feynman Diagrams

Authors: C.D. Palmer and M.E. Carrington

Comments: RevTex 11 pages with 10 figures

Journal-ref: Can.J.Phys. 80 (2002) 847-854

The calculation of the symmetry factor corresponding to a given Feynmandiagram is well known to be a tedious problem. We have derived a simple formulafor these symmetry factors. Our formula works for any diagram in scalar theory($\phi^3$ and $\phi^4$ interactions), spinor QED, scalar QED, or QCD.